data.description: *$1,500 LENDER CREDIT AND FREE APPRAISAL WITH OUR PREFERRED LENDER*Attention Investors! This home offers lots of potential and space. Located close to the downtown area of Centerville. 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths with an additional lot located at 104 Arnold St. (Tax ID: 108l B 013.00) for an extra large yard to entertain in. There is an additional room that use to be the garage and could be finished into a 4th bedroom or office space. Large Den in the walk out basement with Gas Fireplace, additional Full Bath and Bedroom in the basement. Both Lots together equal approx. .40 acres. Selling "As Is" Cash or Conventional Only. Motivated Seller. Bring Offers
